            "id": 5898643,
            "title": "《異動股》國泰跌逾4%,績後遭滙證指面臨增長壓力降評級",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》國泰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00293:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00293\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00293-HK</a>)現價跌4.2%,報10.44元,以現價計,該股暫連跌3日,累計跌幅6.4%。該股成交約2249萬股,涉資2.32億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　國泰昨日中午公布全年業績,截至2024年12月31日止全年股東應佔溢利98.88億元,按年上升1%,好過預期;派發第二次中期息每股0.49元,按年增14%,全年股息增逾六成至69仙。然而期內燃油對沖錄收益較2023年度大減95%至僅3500萬元,在計及對沖收益後,燃油成本淨額按年增加13%倍至282.6億元。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　然而績後國泰遭多行下調目標價或評級,其中滙證指出,未來國泰將要面對貨運禁令與關稅的不利因素,將在今年為國泰的貨計量增長帶來壓力,同時三跑的落成亦會為國泰帶來競爭壓力。該行下調國泰今明兩年的EBIT預測2至4%,將目標價由9.7元降至9.2元,評級由「持有」降至「減持」。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報23550,跌49點或跌0.2%,主板成交近640億元。國企指數報8663,跌19點或跌0.2%。恒生科技指數報5782,跌63點或跌1.1%。即月期指新報23575,跌64點,高水24點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>國泰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00293:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00293\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00293-HK</a>)</td><td>10.44元</td><td>跌4.22%</td></tr><tr><td>國航(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00753:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00753\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00753-HK</a>)</td><td>5.01元</td><td>跌2.34%</td></tr><tr><td>南航(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01055:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01055\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01055-HK</a>)</td><td>3.71元</td><td>跌3.13%</td></tr><tr><td>東航(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00670:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00670\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00670-HK</a>)</td><td>2.57元</td><td>跌0.39%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　(hc)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
